SubmitterDescription.SubmitterName: International Standards For Cytogenomic Arrays Consortium (ISCA)

SampleDescription.Description: unbalanced 9;15 translocation with loss of material on the derivative chromosome 9. The karyotype is best described as: 46,XY,der(9)t(9;15)(q13;q26.3),der(15)t(9;15)(q21.32;q26.3). Phenotype: previous chromosome study with 46,XY,der(9)t(9;15)(q21.2;q26.3),der(15)t(9;15)(q22.1;q26.3), fine and gross motor delay, speech delay, mental retardation, autistic features, dysmorphic facial features, macrocephaly, long digit toes, ataxia, hypotonia
